{"tid":398599,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【分享討論】令人類瘋狂崩潰嘅聲音","createTime":"2017-09-13T10:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T05:00:39.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df3ebf0abb51cf345e190eaf2b77257ac824f447","tid":398599,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"1)不規則嘅高頻嘅聲音<br />\n一聽就毛管戙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心都寒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用手指刮黑板嘅聲識<br />\n係咪因為高頻聲似野獸嘅抓聲<br />\n對原始人類有好大嘅陰影<br />\n所以到而家都仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2)The Hum－低頻但令人崩潰嘅嘈音<br />\n英國每日郵報報導，科學家對是什麼產生了一個名為The Hum（嘈雜聲）的現象感到困惑不已，以及為什麼它隻影響極少數人。只有2%的人能夠聽到這種噪音，它不停歇的嗡嗡聲足以讓人崩潰。受害者報告了相同的因素：嗡嗡聲只能在室內聽到，它是低沉的隆隆聲，在夜晚可能更響亮，常見於農村地區。<br />\n<br />\n來自英國利茲的凱蒂&middot;雅克（Katie Jacques）說道：&ldquo;這真是一種折磨，有時候你只想尖叫。想要入睡真的很困難，我總在背景聲裡聽到心跳聲。你翻來覆去輾轉反側，只會因此變得更加焦慮。&rdquo;能夠聽到這些噪音的人們往往經歷頭痛、噁心、頭暈、流鼻血以及睡眠障礙。英國BBC廣播公司至少報導了一起因這種噪音導致的自殺事件。<br />\n<br />\n一般的Hum噪音受害者的聽力都很正常，當他們離開某一特定區域，這種噪音就消失了。20世紀90年代早期，在新墨西哥Taos小鎮，新墨西哥大學洛薩拉摩斯國家實驗所的一組研究人員無法鑒別Hum的來源。<br />\n雪梨邦迪海灘的一名當地居民說道：&ldquo;這種噪音導致人們都快瘋了，他們不得不聽音樂阻擋這種噪音，有的人就一直讓風扇開著。&rdquo;<br />\n有的人認為這種噪音其實是耳鳴，一種讓病人聽到不存在的聲音的狀況，但人們認為Hum其實是存在的。疑似來源包括工業設備、煤氣管道、電線和無線通信，儘管很少報告事件與它們有關。而其他人則認為這是低頻率電磁輻射或地震活動，例如微震的結果。<br />\n專家建議受害者尋求認知行為療法以幫助處理這種噪音。然而，在短期內解決Hum問題幾乎是不可能的。利文撒爾說道：&ldquo;Hum之謎已經困擾了我們40多年，所以它很可能還將持續下去。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.xuite.net/blog/s120685327/twblog/149160926  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.xuite.net%2Fblog%2Fs120685327%2Ftwblog%2F149160926%20%20&d=Xyb7YRfl%2BF5Ug4SRKlCJ15Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a74e8661\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.xuite.net/blog/s120685327/twblog/149160926  </a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Hum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Hum&d=Xyb7YRfl%2BF5Ug4SRKlCJ15Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=666e9433\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Hum</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b881bfca8b059de217cac9ea553597fc0ae9695b","tid":398599,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1314a74bd7363f0776e7129d5c3e3f5a050295","tid":398599,"uid":34394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"阿蛆嘅天籟之聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889a23614b35d53d5811420a739a0e862d52e24c","tid":398599,"uid":125208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"隔離枱食嘢既zip zip聲"},{"pid":"7b2c2aa269efb5fe3f6256e53a2f7c48a88623d5","tid":398599,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:23:42.000Z","msg":"一路屌條女但條女喺度叫個ex 既名"},{"pid":"bf2849652b9ab184d956ddf421439a5bcd045c5d","tid":398599,"uid":135019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿蛆嘅天籟之聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8rCcQed7DE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du8rCcQed7DE&d=Xyb7YRfl%2BF5Ug4SRKlCJ15Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=58e81586\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8rCcQed7DE</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1a62d89e9465a9eedb7358aece503836c912e8","tid":398599,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿蛆嘅天籟之聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.g